%h2 Import

= form_tag({controller: 'imports', action: 'create'}, method: 'post', multipart: true) do

  %p.my-20
    The import process allows you to upload a zip file (maximum 1 Gb) containing several items and documents in one step.
    Please ensure that filenames within your collection are unique.
    <a href="http://alveo.edu.au/help/uploading-data-to-a-collection/">See here for help</a> with the structure of your zip file.

  = label_tag :zip_file, 'File:'
  = file_field_tag 'zip_file', :class => ""

  = render 'collections/display_additional_metadata'

  .form-actions
    = submit_tag 'Upload', :class => "btn btn-primary"
    = link_to 'Cancel', collection_path(@collection.name), :class => "btn"

= render 'shared/nectar_attribution'
